    A hunter is looking for assistance with a rare creature
    A hunter is looking for assistance with a dangerous creature
    A hunter is looking for assistance hunting a unique creature
    A hunter is looking for assistance obtaining a rare creatures egg/offspring.
    A dragon-slayer would like information on local dragons.
    A jolly man invites you fishing.
    A talking snake wishes for you to bring him several moon rats to eat.
    A creature that is undocumented has been spotted to the west.
    An extremely rare creature was spotted just outside town.

