    A lich has been raising zombies to do menial labor, locals are uneasy.
    Local acolytes want to perform rituals on the locals, the process is very painful.
    A wizard wants help convincing the townsfolk that his spell is actually a natural phenomena.
    The party is called to investigate a mystery.

